Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.27,0:02:53.89,OP_Ro,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.5}Urami wa tachidomarasu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.89,0:02:56.30,OP_Ro,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.5}Are wa boku no sei ni shi na
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.30,0:02:58.92,OP_Ro,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.5}Sore mo boku no sei ni shite yo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.92,0:03:04.01,OP_Ro,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.5}Kimi o zutto tachitomeru sono subete to
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.01,0:03:09.64,OP_Ro,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.5}Boku igai o yurushite susunde yuki na yo
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.25,0:03:19.20,OP_Ro,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.5}Shougai kareru koto no nai hana to nazukete mo
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.20,0:03:24.27,OP_Ro,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.5}Shougai kareru koto no nai hana ni naru koto wa nai
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.96,0:03:29.27,OP_Ro,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.5}Majime ni ikiteireba itsuka mukuwareru
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.88,0:03:34.30,OP_Ro,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.5}Sou yatte iikitteshimaeba sore wa uso ni naru
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.30,0:03:39.41,OP_Ro,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.5}Mi ni okoru sono suujuppaasento jigoujitoku demo
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.41,0:03:44.47,OP_Ro,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.5}Nokori no suupaasento dare no sei demo nai sono fubyoudou
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.47,0:03:49.65,OP_Ro,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.5}Ichiban ikenai koto wa sa
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.65,0:03:54.50,OP_Ro,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.5}Jibun wa dame da to omou koto
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.50,0:03:56.97,OP_Ro,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.5}Are wa boku no sei ni shi na
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.97,0:03:59.53,OP_Ro,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.5}Sore mo boku no sei ni shite yo
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.53,0:04:04.61,OP_Ro,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.5}Boku igai o yurushite susunde yuki na yo
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.61,0:04:10.60,OP_Ro,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.5}Kimi jishin no koto mo yurushiteagete yo
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.09,0:02:49.27,OP_Vie,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.5}Tha thứ để bước tiếp.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.27,0:02:53.89,OP_Vie,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.5}Hận thù sẽ làm bạn dừng bước.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.89,0:02:56.30,OP_Vie,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.5}Chuyện đó hãy đổ lỗi sang tôi nhé.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.30,0:02:58.92,OP_Vie,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.5}Chuyện này cũng đổ lỗi sang cho tôi đi.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.92,0:03:04.01,OP_Vie,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.5}Tất cả những thứ cản bước bạn bấy lâu
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.01,0:03:09.64,OP_Vie,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.5}Hãy để đó cho riêng mình tôi và bước tiếp đi.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.25,0:03:19.20,OP_Vie,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.5}Dù có gọi tên mình là bông hoa tàn úa.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.20,0:03:24.27,OP_Vie,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.5}Thì cũng chẳng thể trở thành bông hoa tàn úa đó đâu.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.96,0:03:29.27,OP_Vie,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.5}Cứ sống hết mình thì ắt sẽ được khen thưởng.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.88,0:03:34.30,OP_Vie,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.5}Nhưng nếu vì thế mà sống thì chuyện đó lại thành lời nói dối đó.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.30,0:03:39.41,OP_Vie,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1.5}Mọi chuyện diễn ra có vài chục phần trăm là tự làm tự chịu thôi.
